//
// test/sema/resolution/proc_method.test — `inst.finish()` /
// `inst.invoke()` proc-method form per N6/S21 (T023 rollover;
// specs/006-m3-sema/tasks.md Phase 4a). Asserts that the parser
// emits a control-call expression whose head is the proc instance
// (Phase 4b T059 / S21 will refine the kind validation; this
// fixture pins the Phase-3 resolution shape).
//
// Per `emit-ast-format.contract.md` Invariants 2 + 3 (ASCII
// separators per Invariant 7).

// RUN: printf 'module m {\n  proc_name p;\n  proc p {\n    finish;\n  }\n}\n' > %t.nsl
// RUN: %nslc -emit=ast %t.nsl | FileCheck %s

// CHECK: (ModuleBlock {{.*}}name=m
// CHECK: (ProcNameDecl {{.*}}name=p
// CHECK: (ProcDefn {{.*}}name=p
